                </div>
                <p>Volunteering during natural calamities involves providing aid and support to affected communities
                    through rescue efforts, relief distribution, and rebuilding

                    Such acts of service demonstrate compassion, resilience, and solidarity in times of crisis.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/opportunitiesWomenEmpowerment">
